OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FVeteran comedian Martin Short has
OL,7,Fopened up about the "nightmare for his
OL,8,Ffamily" after the death of his
OL,9,Fdaughter earlier this year.
OL,11,FKatherine Short died by suicide in
OL,12,FFebruary at the age of 42, and Short
OL,13,Fdiscussed the impact it had on him and
OL,14,Fhis family with CBS News on Sunday.
OL,16,FThe 76-year-old actor spoke about how
OL,17,Fhe handled the grief and compared the
OL,18,Fexperience with the loss of his wife,
OL,19,FNancy Dolman, who died of ovarian
OL,20,Fcancer in 2010.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
