OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FHe said he understood them the same
OL,7,Fway, saying, "mental health and
OL,8,Fcancer, like my wife's, are both
OL,9,Fdiseases, and sometimes with diseases
OL,10,Fthey are terminal and my daughter
OL,11,Ffought for a long time with extreme
OL,12,Fmental health, borderline personality
OL,13,Fdisorder, other things, and did the
OL,14,Fbest she could, until she couldn't."
OL,16,FHe went on to say: "So, Nan's last
OL,17,Fwords to me were, 'Martin, let me go.'
OL,18,FAnd what (Katherine) was just saying,
OL,19,F'Dad, let me go.'"
