OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FKatherine was the eldest of three
OL,7,Fchildren adopted by Short and Dolman.
OL,8,FShe studied psychology and gender
OL,9,Fsexuality studies from New York
OL,10,FUniversity in 2006 and also earned a
OL,11,Fmaster's in social work.
OL,13,FShe spent most of her life working in
OL,14,Fprivate practice and keeping out of
OL,15,Fthe spotlight, only occasionally
OL,16,Fappearing alongside her father on the
OL,17,Fred carpet.
OL,19,FShort was speaking to CBS ahead of the
OL,20,Frelease of a Netflix documentary about
OL,21,Fhis life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
