OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMarty: Life Is Short, is due out this
OL,12,Fweek and is directed by Hollywood
OL,13,Flegend and Short's close friend
OL,14,FLawrence Kasdan.
OL,16,FA lot of the documentary focuses on
OL,17,Fthe trials Short has gone through in
OL,18,Flife, with him suffering numerous
OL,19,Ftragedies from a young age.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
