OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FHis older brother David died in a car
OL,7,Fcrash when he was 12, and both of his
OL,8,Fparents died when he was a teenager.
OL,10,FAlongside the loss of his wife and
OL,11,Fdaughter, he has also had several
OL,12,Fclose friends die in recent years,
OL,13,Fincluding Diane Keaton, Rob and
OL,14,FMichele Reiner and Catherine O'Hara.
OL,16,FHe told CBS the loss of so many people
OL,17,Fin such a short amount of time was
OL,18,F"staggering", adding: "You just have
OL,19,Fto breathe in, breathe out."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
