OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FDespite the hardship, Short has a well-
OL,7,Fknown reputation for being a happy
OL,8,Fperson who often brings joy to the
OL,9,Froom.
OL,11,FHe told CBS: "I think I do have the
OL,12,Fhappy gene and I think my orientation
OL,13,Fis to be happy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
