OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778526672
OL,3,CMartin Short opens up about
OL,4,C'nightmare' of daughter's death
OL,6,FShort said the loss of loved ones led
OL,7,Fto him developing this muscle of
OL,8,Fsurvival and handling grief and a
OL,9,Fperspective on it", as well as the
OL,10,Fbravery to become a performer: "I
OL,11,Fthink if you've gone through that, an
OL,12,Faudience not liking you is really not
OL,13,Fthat important any more."
